ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='final_result', args='{""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/1.3/Brick#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone WHERE {\\n  # Zone classification\\n  ?zone a brick:Zone .\\n\\n  # Either a direct property relationship\\n  {\\n    ?zone ?directRel ?prop .\\n    ?prop a brick:Property .\\n  }\\n  UNION\\n  # Or an indirect connection via a RoomDomainSpace (any length of relationship hops)\\n  {\\n    # Navigate from the zone to any RoomDomainSpace through any chain of predicates\\n    ?zone ( ?* ) ?rds .\\n    ?rds a brick:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    # From that RoomDomainSpace navigate to a Property through any chain of predicates\\n    ?rds ( ?* ) ?prop .\\n    ?prop a brick:Property .\\n  }\\n}\\n""}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-b0b867c721e94074b0144ebc35a215b6', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 21, 17, 40, 38, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
